M||tx|---
M||titl|useEffectEvent for Stable Callback Refs
M||impa|lo
M||impa|prevents effect re-runs
M||tags|advanced, hooks, useEffectEvent, refs, op
M||tx|---
M|useE|tx|Access latest values in callbacks w/o adding them to dependency arrays. Prevents effect re-runs while avoiding stale closures.
M|useE|**In|**
M|useE|tx|```tsx
M|useE|func|{ onSearch: (q: string) => void }) {
M|useE|tx|const [query, setQuery] = useState('')
M|useE|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|useE|tx|const timeout = setTimeout(() => onSearch(query), 300)
M|useE|tx|return () => clearTimeout(timeout)
M|useE|tx|}, [query, onSearch])
M|useE|tx|}
M|useE|tx|```
M|useE|**Co|**
M|useE|tx|```tsx
M|useE|tx|import { useEffectEvent } from 'rc';
M|useE|func|{ onSearch: (q: string) => void }) {
M|useE|tx|const [query, setQuery] = useState('')
M|useE|tx|const onSearchEvent = useEffectEvent(onSearch)
M|useE|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|useE|tx|const timeout = setTimeout(() => onSearchEvent(query), 300)
M|useE|tx|return () => clearTimeout(timeout)
M|useE|tx|}, [query])
M|useE|tx|}
M|useE|tx|```